      "Text": "Security update for the Linux Kernel",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "\nThe SUSE Linux Enterprise 12 SP1 kernel was updated to 3.12.74 to receive\nthe following security fix:\n\n- CVE-2017-7533: Bug in inotify code allowed privilege escalation (bnc#1049483).\n",
